WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 13=

00:01:38.460 --> 00:01:41.580 line:80%
(Xuanwu Altar, Dungeon)

00:01:45.540 --> 00:01:47.780 line:80%
(Li Sect, Xing)

00:01:47.780 --> 00:01:48.620 line:80%
Hurry.

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:49.540 line:80%
Come on, open up!

00:01:50.010 --> 00:01:51.210 line:80%
Can't get it open.

00:01:54.130 --> 00:01:55.090 line:80%
What a useless door!

00:01:55.460 --> 00:01:56.570 line:80%
This is driving me crazy.

00:02:00.090 --> 00:02:01.210 line:80%
So filthy in here.

00:02:04.700 --> 00:02:05.540 line:80%
Xing.

00:02:06.420 --> 00:02:07.260 line:80%
Listen!

00:02:07.270 --> 00:02:08.370 line:80%
Using me to threaten You Guanyue

00:02:08.370 --> 00:02:09.460 line:80%
is totally useless.

00:02:09.550 --> 00:02:10.490 line:80%
If he dares back down,

00:02:10.520 --> 00:02:11.420 line:80%
I'll tear him a new one!

00:02:16.860 --> 00:02:18.190 line:80%
Xing, I'm here to rescue you.

00:02:18.210 --> 00:02:19.050 line:80%
Come with me.

00:02:20.090 --> 00:02:20.930 line:80%
Go.

00:02:24.740 --> 00:02:26.660 line:80%
(Master of Xuanwu Altar, Xiong Qianjin)

00:02:27.020 --> 00:02:27.900 line:80%
I'd like to see

00:02:28.300 --> 00:02:29.140 line:80%
who this

00:02:29.300 --> 00:02:30.410 line:80%
spy is.

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:34.700 line:80%
Find a chance to escape.

00:03:03.340 --> 00:03:04.180 line:80%
Where's Xing?

00:03:04.250 --> 00:03:05.090 line:80%
She ran away.

00:03:05.090 --> 00:03:05.970 line:80%
Where to?

00:03:06.180 --> 00:03:07.020 line:80%
You didn't see her?

00:03:42.250 --> 00:03:43.090 line:80%
Get up!

00:03:46.060 --> 00:03:46.900 line:80%
Go!

00:03:58.710 --> 00:04:00.180 line:80%
Mu Qingyan seized the Qinglong Altar.

00:04:00.410 --> 00:04:02.580 line:80%
Nie Zhe will surely set up
heavy guards all around.

00:04:03.180 --> 00:04:04.860 line:80%
We need a foolproof plan first.

00:04:05.810 --> 00:04:07.650 line:80%
Say our family works at
the Qinglong Altar,

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:09.620 line:80%
and we're here to
persuade them to surrender.

00:04:10.750 --> 00:04:11.740 line:80%
The demon sect is ruthless.

00:04:12.580 --> 00:04:13.900 line:80%
They won't spare innocents,

00:04:14.250 --> 00:04:15.090 line:80%
let alone relatives.

00:04:16.140 --> 00:04:17.260 line:80%
This plan is too risky.

00:04:18.700 --> 00:04:19.700 line:80%
Stories always say,

00:04:19.900 --> 00:04:20.940 line:80%
victory favors the bold.

00:04:21.410 --> 00:04:22.850 line:80%
Only the brave win head-on fights.

00:04:23.850 --> 00:04:25.380 line:80%
You'll never know unless you try.

00:04:26.140 --> 00:04:26.980 line:80%
Zhao.

00:04:26.990 --> 00:04:28.780 line:80%
You can't survive out there
just by storybooks.

00:04:30.610 --> 00:04:32.210 line:80%
Books pave the way for journeys.

00:04:32.530 --> 00:04:33.370 line:80%
Why wouldn't it work?

00:04:34.050 --> 00:04:34.890 line:80%
Hurry up and go.

00:04:43.210 --> 00:04:44.230 line:80%
- A ghost!
- Don't run!

00:04:44.260 --> 00:04:45.100 line:80%
A ghost!

00:04:45.460 --> 00:04:46.860 line:80%
- Miss!
-Ghost! Ghost!

00:04:46.900 --> 00:04:47.740 line:80%
Miss.

00:04:48.290 --> 00:04:49.130 line:80%
Miss!

00:04:53.820 --> 00:04:54.900 line:80%
(No inner power at all)

00:04:55.940 --> 00:04:56.780 line:80%
Calm down.

00:04:56.790 --> 00:04:57.820 line:80%
What kind of ghost was it?

00:04:58.410 --> 00:04:59.250 line:80%
Take your time.

00:04:59.700 --> 00:05:01.050 line:80%
I saw a bunch of walking ghosts.

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:02.220 line:80%
Yellow faces.

00:05:02.530 --> 00:05:03.370 line:80%
White eyes.

00:05:03.610 --> 00:05:04.500 line:80%
They walk like this.

00:05:06.340 --> 00:05:07.180 line:80%
It terrified me.

00:05:08.500 --> 00:05:09.650 line:80%
Could it be the corpse slaves?

00:05:09.870 --> 00:05:11.500 line:80%
Could Nie Zhe be up to
his old tricks again,

00:05:11.730 --> 00:05:13.020 line:80%
refining corpse slaves once more?

00:05:14.050 --> 00:05:14.890 line:80%
Who are you?

00:05:17.460 --> 00:05:19.020 line:80%
Why are you wearing my dress?

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:21.850 line:80%
Village chief gave it to me.

00:05:22.650 --> 00:05:23.490 line:80%
Grandpa?

00:05:23.580 --> 00:05:24.420 line:80%
You're Xing?

00:05:24.780 --> 00:05:25.620 line:80%
Enough.

00:05:25.620 --> 00:05:26.650 line:80%
I need to tell Grandpa quickly.

00:05:26.650 --> 00:05:27.610 line:80%
If Xiong Qianjin comes for me,

00:05:27.610 --> 00:05:28.530 line:80%
everyone will be in trouble.

00:05:29.610 --> 00:05:30.450 line:80%
Xing!

00:05:31.940 --> 00:05:32.900 line:80%
We'll go with you.

00:05:57.820 --> 00:05:59.410 line:80%
Where did you hide Xing?

00:06:00.970 --> 00:06:01.810 line:80%
No idea.

00:06:02.210 --> 00:06:03.170 line:80%
I don't know.

00:06:03.170 --> 00:06:04.010 line:80%
No idea.

00:06:06.700 --> 00:06:08.260 line:80%
Tell me where you hid Xing!

00:06:12.020 --> 00:06:13.170 line:80%
Tell me!

00:06:16.260 --> 00:06:17.100 line:80%
If you do,

00:06:17.610 --> 00:06:18.970 line:80%
then you won't die.

00:06:18.970 --> 00:06:20.580 line:80%
Xiong Qianjin, you scoundrel!

00:06:20.900 --> 00:06:21.740 line:80%
I...

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:26.620 line:80%
Keep this safe for me.

00:06:27.340 --> 00:06:28.340 line:80%
Zhao, what are you doing?

00:06:28.610 --> 00:06:29.450 line:80%
Don't worry, Yuzhi.

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:30.620 line:80%
Gotta disguise myself.

00:06:39.260 --> 00:06:40.290 line:80%
Where did you hide Xing?

00:06:40.850 --> 00:06:42.900 line:80%
I don't know. I really don't know.

00:06:50.580 --> 00:06:51.700 line:80%
You all wanna die, huh?

00:06:53.610 --> 00:06:54.450 line:80%
Speak!

00:07:00.780 --> 00:07:01.620 line:80%
Stop!

00:07:05.610 --> 00:07:06.450 line:80%
Xiong Qianjin.

00:07:06.630 --> 00:07:07.730 line:80%
Aren't you here to catch me?

00:07:11.460 --> 00:07:12.300 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:07:12.700 --> 00:07:13.540 line:80%
Let them go.

00:07:26.370 --> 00:07:28.050 line:80%
Grandpa, don't be scared.

00:07:28.170 --> 00:07:29.010 line:80%
It'll be fine.

00:07:37.020 --> 00:07:37.940 line:80%
Xing.

00:07:38.140 --> 00:07:40.020 line:80%
They killed Wang.

00:07:40.020 --> 00:07:41.260 line:80%
Poor Wang.

00:07:41.260 --> 00:07:43.210 line:80%
He barely lived in his new house.

00:07:43.210 --> 00:07:44.050 line:80%
Shut up!

00:07:48.050 --> 00:07:48.890 line:80%
Big lug.

00:07:48.920 --> 00:07:50.050 line:80%
Aren't you gonna take me away?

00:07:50.140 --> 00:07:51.180 line:80%
What are you stalling for?

00:07:53.290 --> 00:07:55.020 line:80%
I hate being called a big lug.

00:07:55.700 --> 00:07:56.700 line:80%
If you try to run again,

00:07:57.340 --> 00:07:58.290 line:80%
I'll break your legs!

00:07:59.970 --> 00:08:00.810 line:80%
Come on.

00:08:01.170 --> 00:08:02.050 line:80%
Take them all back!

00:08:02.530 --> 00:08:03.900 line:80%
Wait.

00:08:04.260 --> 00:08:05.890 line:80%
Move, hurry!

00:08:09.940 --> 00:08:10.780 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:08:12.530 --> 00:08:13.370 line:80%
Hurry!

00:08:24.020 --> 00:08:25.850 line:80%
Xing.

00:08:25.850 --> 00:08:27.170 line:80%
Grandpa, Grandpa.

00:08:27.670 --> 00:08:29.090 line:80%
Go to Qinglong Altar for reinforcements.

00:08:29.610 --> 00:08:30.450 line:80%
I'll save Zhao.

00:08:37.570 --> 00:08:38.410 line:80%
Go! Hurry!

00:08:40.140 --> 00:08:41.100 line:80%
Keep up, back there!

00:08:41.930 --> 00:08:42.770 line:80%
Hurry!

00:08:44.220 --> 00:08:45.060 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:08:47.220 --> 00:08:48.060 line:80%
Go!

00:08:55.330 --> 00:08:56.170 line:80%
Go!

00:08:56.380 --> 00:08:57.220 line:80%
Keep up!

00:09:02.780 --> 00:09:03.620 line:80%
Hurry!

00:09:10.100 --> 00:09:10.940 line:80%
Hurry!

00:09:13.140 --> 00:09:13.980 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:09:15.380 --> 00:09:16.930 line:80%
You nearly blinded me.

00:09:17.020 --> 00:09:18.290 line:80%
One day, I'll take your eyes out!

00:09:18.530 --> 00:09:19.860 line:80%
Master Xiong.

00:09:26.450 --> 00:09:27.290 line:80%
Lady Sun.

00:09:27.810 --> 00:09:28.690 line:80%
It's so late.

00:09:29.020 --> 00:09:30.930 line:80%
What brings you to such a remote place?

00:09:31.980 --> 00:09:33.410 line:80%
Picking flowers for the Chief.

00:09:34.650 --> 00:09:36.900 line:80%
These flowers need night dew

00:09:37.450 --> 00:09:38.650 line:80%
to have their medicinal effect.

00:09:39.170 --> 00:09:40.220 line:80%
- Move quickly!
- Yes.

00:09:54.260 --> 00:09:55.170 line:80%
Who are you?

00:09:55.950 --> 00:09:57.220 line:80%
I'm a maid of the Qinglong Altar.

00:09:57.570 --> 00:09:58.410 line:80%
Xing.

00:09:58.410 --> 00:09:59.530 line:80%
Your face is covered in dirt,

00:09:59.980 --> 00:10:01.500 line:80%
but your eyes are beautiful.

00:10:05.780 --> 00:10:06.740 line:80%
Master Xiong.

00:10:07.260 --> 00:10:09.570 line:80%
Why not give this girl to me?

00:10:10.690 --> 00:10:11.530 line:80%
This...

00:10:12.220 --> 00:10:13.060 line:80%
Madam.

00:10:13.220 --> 00:10:14.570 line:80%
The strategist asked for this girl.

00:10:14.980 --> 00:10:16.740 line:80%
I'm afraid I can't explain it to him.

00:10:18.410 --> 00:10:19.250 line:80%
Fine then.

00:10:22.900 --> 00:10:23.740 line:80%
Farewell, Madam.

00:10:25.690 --> 00:10:27.020 line:80%
Quit staring! Move!

00:10:38.620 --> 00:10:39.460 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:10:40.520 --> 00:10:41.780 line:80%
The village is completely empty.

00:10:42.050 --> 00:10:43.220 line:80%
Xing is nowhere to be found.

00:10:43.620 --> 00:10:44.810 line:80%
Where exactly did Xing go?

00:11:10.780 --> 00:11:11.620 line:80%
Find them.

00:11:34.260 --> 00:11:37.260 line:80%
(Youming Path)

00:11:41.740 --> 00:11:42.580 line:80%
Move!

00:12:04.260 --> 00:12:05.100 line:80%
My leg!

00:12:07.020 --> 00:12:07.860 line:80%
My leg.

00:12:09.290 --> 00:12:10.740 line:80%
I can't go on either.

00:12:13.380 --> 00:12:14.220 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:12:14.550 --> 00:12:15.490 line:80%
Are you trying to die?

00:12:16.050 --> 00:12:17.500 line:80%
My old leg injury is acting up again.

00:12:17.520 --> 00:12:18.690 line:80%
- I can't walk anymore.
- Get up.

00:12:19.140 --> 00:12:20.260 line:80%
My knee's acting up again.

00:12:20.740 --> 00:12:21.580 line:80%
I can't move.

00:12:21.930 --> 00:12:22.780 line:80%
Stand up!

00:12:22.780 --> 00:12:23.900 line:80%
Get up now, hear me?

00:12:25.500 --> 00:12:26.340 line:80%
Dare to run?

00:12:26.770 --> 00:12:27.780 line:80%
- Come back!
- After her!

00:12:27.900 --> 00:12:28.740 line:80%
Catch her!

00:12:30.140 --> 00:12:30.980 line:80%
Stop!

00:12:31.530 --> 00:12:32.370 line:80%
Don't run!

00:12:40.020 --> 00:12:40.860 line:80%
Stop!

00:12:42.330 --> 00:12:43.170 line:80%
Over there!

00:12:59.500 --> 00:13:01.980 line:80%
This is the Poison Swarm Array
aunt encountered back then.

00:13:05.170 --> 00:13:06.650 line:80%
Touch the array's trigger,

00:13:09.930 --> 00:13:12.220 line:80%
and deadly venomous swarm
will swarm you.

00:13:13.260 --> 00:13:14.100 line:80%
Run!

00:13:14.260 --> 00:13:15.140 line:80%
Once they sting you,

00:13:15.140 --> 00:13:16.170 line:80%
(Spring and Blossoms)

00:13:16.170 --> 00:13:17.170 line:80%
you'll die for sure.

00:13:18.100 --> 00:13:18.940 line:80%
(This array)

00:13:19.450 --> 00:13:21.410 line:80%
(is just like the Poison Swarm Array)

00:13:21.740 --> 00:13:22.650 line:80%
(aunt told me about.)

00:13:28.860 --> 00:13:30.500 line:80%
(This must be the trigger spot.)

00:13:33.260 --> 00:13:35.290 line:80%
As long as I apply
the Bee-Repelling Powder,

00:13:35.860 --> 00:13:37.500 line:80%
the venomous bees will stay far away.

00:13:43.540 --> 00:13:44.980 line:80%
There she is! Don't let her get away!

00:14:11.860 --> 00:14:12.700 line:80%
Stay still!

00:14:36.450 --> 00:14:37.290 line:80%
You guys go, now.

00:14:37.980 --> 00:14:39.930 line:80%
But what about Miss Feng?

00:14:40.190 --> 00:14:41.130 line:80%
I'll get you out first.

00:14:41.950 --> 00:14:43.290 line:80%
This is what Miss Feng wanted too.

00:14:44.380 --> 00:14:45.690 line:80%
Alright, let's go.

00:14:45.810 --> 00:14:46.740 line:80%
Go, let's go.

00:14:47.170 --> 00:14:48.010 line:80%
- Go.
- Go!

00:14:48.410 --> 00:14:49.290 line:80%
Hurry, go now!

00:14:55.530 --> 00:14:56.370 line:80%
Who are you?

00:15:07.740 --> 00:15:08.580 line:80%
You're not Xing.

00:15:22.740 --> 00:15:23.650 line:80%
(Oh no.)

00:15:24.020 --> 00:15:27.220 line:80%
(She fed me softening powder.)

00:15:32.810 --> 00:15:33.650 line:80%
Don't try any tricks.

00:15:34.620 --> 00:15:35.460 line:80%
Move!

00:15:41.620 --> 00:15:46.020 line:80%
(Li Sect, EightClaw Prison)

00:16:13.450 --> 00:16:14.290 line:80%
Speak.

00:16:14.830 --> 00:16:15.820 line:80%
Who are your accomplices?

00:16:16.740 --> 00:16:17.810 line:80%
Six Sects of Beichen,

00:16:18.570 --> 00:16:19.500 line:80%
or Mu Qingyan?

00:16:22.380 --> 00:16:23.530 line:80%
I don't know them.

00:16:24.450 --> 00:16:26.530 line:80%
I'm just a junior from the Qingzhu Gang.

00:16:27.020 --> 00:16:27.930 line:80%
I came to the Li Sect

00:16:28.740 --> 00:16:30.140 line:80%
to seek refuge with a relative.

00:16:30.930 --> 00:16:31.940 line:80%
Qingzhu Gang?

00:16:32.310 --> 00:16:33.370 line:80%
Our Qingzhu Gang

00:16:33.530 --> 00:16:35.690 line:80%
is a small sect by the Canglang River.

00:16:36.380 --> 00:16:37.330 line:80%
The leader passed away.

00:16:37.980 --> 00:16:39.050 line:80%
And the sect disbanded.

00:16:40.530 --> 00:16:41.530 line:80%
I had nowhere else to go.

00:16:42.450 --> 00:16:43.900 line:80%
So I came here to find my relative.

00:16:49.690 --> 00:16:50.930 line:80%
Why did you pretend to be Xing?

00:16:54.290 --> 00:16:55.620 line:80%
I got lost in the forest.

00:16:56.530 --> 00:16:58.100 line:80%
The villagers found me

00:16:58.100 --> 00:16:58.940 line:80%
and took me in.

00:16:59.930 --> 00:17:01.170 line:80%
If it weren't for them,

00:17:02.260 --> 00:17:03.500 line:80%
I would've died a long time ago.

00:17:04.320 --> 00:17:05.460 line:80%
My martial arts aren't great,

00:17:06.330 --> 00:17:07.220 line:80%
but I do understand

00:17:08.320 --> 00:17:09.260 line:80%
a small act of kindness

00:17:09.320 --> 00:17:10.810 line:80%
should be repaid with deep gratitude.

00:17:11.810 --> 00:17:12.650 line:80%
Last night,

00:17:13.220 --> 00:17:14.530 line:80%
that so-called Master Xiong

00:17:15.220 --> 00:17:16.460 line:80%
tied up everyone in the village.

00:17:17.260 --> 00:17:18.120 line:80%
He said

00:17:18.180 --> 00:17:19.370 line:80%
if they didn't hand over Xing,

00:17:19.700 --> 00:17:21.530 line:80%
he'd kill every single one of them.

00:17:23.940 --> 00:17:25.850 line:80%
He killed Uncle Wang
right then and there.

00:17:26.570 --> 00:17:28.020 line:80%
It was a horrifying scene.

00:17:29.130 --> 00:17:30.740 line:80%
They saved my life.

00:17:30.940 --> 00:17:32.260 line:80%
How could I stand by and do nothing?

00:17:34.020 --> 00:17:34.860 line:80%
I acted on impulse,

00:17:36.530 --> 00:17:37.780 line:80%
and pretended to be Xing.

00:17:39.090 --> 00:17:40.610 line:80%
Xiong Qianjin.

00:17:41.370 --> 00:17:43.530 line:80%
He used the villagers' lives
to threaten us.

00:17:45.370 --> 00:17:46.210 line:80%
Yeah.

00:17:47.740 --> 00:17:49.090 line:80%
Poor Uncle Wang.

00:17:49.660 --> 00:17:51.090 line:80%
His baby was only three months old.

00:17:51.610 --> 00:17:53.740 line:80%
Aunt Wang cried so hard
she almost fainted.

00:18:01.740 --> 00:18:02.580 line:80%
You're lying.

00:18:03.220 --> 00:18:05.260 line:80%
How could a mere Qingzhu clan disciple

00:18:05.610 --> 00:18:07.090 line:80%
know about the Poison Swarm Array?

00:18:09.570 --> 00:18:10.410 line:80%
Sis.

00:18:11.740 --> 00:18:12.780 line:80%
You don't know.

00:18:14.050 --> 00:18:15.850 line:80%
When our leader was young,

00:18:15.870 --> 00:18:17.180 line:80%
he had an extraordinary experience.

00:18:17.890 --> 00:18:19.090 line:80%
He said he once met a

00:18:19.090 --> 00:18:20.660 line:80%
most amazing female hero.

00:18:21.660 --> 00:18:22.610 line:80%
That heroine

00:18:23.050 --> 00:18:23.980 line:80%
wielded a sword

00:18:24.420 --> 00:18:25.810 line:80%
brighter than the sun.

00:18:26.260 --> 00:18:27.100 line:80%
So mighty.

00:18:28.020 --> 00:18:29.130 line:80%
That array

00:18:29.810 --> 00:18:31.980 line:80%
was taught to our old leader
by the heroine.

00:18:33.220 --> 00:18:34.260 line:80%
Could it be her?

00:18:35.530 --> 00:18:37.370 line:80%
(This person doesn't seem all that bad.)

00:18:38.890 --> 00:18:39.730 line:80%
Sis.

00:18:40.780 --> 00:18:41.620 line:80%
Is this place

00:18:41.890 --> 00:18:43.220 line:80%
where they

00:18:43.610 --> 00:18:45.420 line:80%
turn people into monsters?

00:18:45.610 --> 00:18:46.450 line:80%
What monsters?

00:18:51.370 --> 00:18:52.330 line:80%
The village chief said,

00:18:52.850 --> 00:18:53.850 line:80%
lately in the village,

00:18:54.180 --> 00:18:56.460 line:80%
when the uncles and brothers go hunting,

00:18:57.030 --> 00:18:58.700 line:80%
they keep getting captured
by the Slayer Ghost.

00:18:59.320 --> 00:19:00.890 line:80%
When they come back,
they're turned into

00:19:00.890 --> 00:19:01.940 line:80%
gray-faced, white-eyed monsters.

00:19:02.660 --> 00:19:03.740 line:80%
Slayer Ghost?

00:19:03.850 --> 00:19:04.690 line:80%
Yeah.

00:19:04.810 --> 00:19:05.650 line:80%
It's terrifying.

00:19:06.940 --> 00:19:08.500 line:80%
Neither alive nor dead.

00:19:08.840 --> 00:19:09.810 line:80%
No response when called.

00:19:09.980 --> 00:19:11.660 line:80%
And it suddenly
goes mad and bites people.

00:19:12.570 --> 00:19:13.410 line:80%
Sis.

00:19:25.220 --> 00:19:26.530 line:80%
You're refining a corpse slave.

00:19:27.780 --> 00:19:29.130 line:80%
Back then, Master lost his mind,

00:19:29.720 --> 00:19:31.220 line:80%
and insisted on refining corpse slaves.

00:19:31.660 --> 00:19:33.700 line:80%
Our fellow disciples
either died or scattered.

00:19:33.850 --> 00:19:34.940 line:80%
Have you forgotten all that?

00:19:36.180 --> 00:19:38.180 line:80%
Why are you making these
evil things again?

00:19:40.260 --> 00:19:41.100 line:80%
I haven't forgotten.

00:19:42.290 --> 00:19:43.710 line:80%
But this is the Chief's order.

00:19:45.230 --> 00:19:46.420 line:80%
I have no choice but to obey.

00:19:47.030 --> 00:19:48.290 line:80%
The ambush on the Six Sects earlier

00:19:48.660 --> 00:19:50.460 line:80%
cost the Demonic Camp heavy losses.

00:19:50.980 --> 00:19:52.500 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is advancing fast,

00:19:53.220 --> 00:19:54.940 line:80%
and the sect is severely short-handed.

00:19:55.180 --> 00:19:56.700 line:80%
I had no other option.

00:19:56.710 --> 00:19:58.420 line:80%
But you can't
use innocent villagers' lives.

00:19:59.320 --> 00:20:01.500 line:80%
Their families have supported
the Li Sect for generations.

00:20:02.130 --> 00:20:03.530 line:80%
The Li Sect should protect them,

00:20:03.740 --> 00:20:05.290 line:80%
not refine them into corpses.

00:20:08.180 --> 00:20:11.130 line:80%
That village has secretly
sided with the Six Sects,

00:20:11.180 --> 00:20:12.660 line:80%
passing them information.

00:20:12.660 --> 00:20:13.500 line:80%
They must be dealt with.

00:20:17.810 --> 00:20:18.740 line:80%
Fengge.

00:20:18.940 --> 00:20:19.780 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:20:20.890 --> 00:20:22.290 line:80%
For those loyal to the Li Sect,

00:20:22.740 --> 00:20:24.610 line:80%
we will protect them well.

00:20:35.460 --> 00:20:36.300 line:80%
Fengge.

00:20:38.460 --> 00:20:39.980 line:80%
I will investigate myself

00:20:41.050 --> 00:20:42.370 line:80%
whether they betrayed the Li Sect.

00:20:57.020 --> 00:20:57.860 line:80%
Find the one

00:20:58.330 --> 00:20:59.980 line:80%
who leaked the news to Elder Hu.

00:21:01.740 --> 00:21:02.580 line:80%
Kill them.

00:21:03.330 --> 00:21:04.170 line:80%
Understood.

00:21:23.050 --> 00:21:23.890 line:80%
Peng bird.

00:21:57.570 --> 00:21:59.530 line:80%
(Youming Path)

00:22:00.180 --> 00:22:01.850 line:80%
(EightClaw Prison)

00:22:19.300 --> 00:22:25.380 line:80%
(Guo Zigui)

00:22:28.530 --> 00:22:29.890 line:80%
Guo Zigui.

00:22:30.500 --> 00:22:31.850 line:80%
Uncle Guo.

00:22:40.220 --> 00:22:41.460 line:80%
Mom's the best!

00:22:41.610 --> 00:22:42.890 line:80%
Mom's the best!

00:22:42.890 --> 00:22:44.460 line:80%
Your Uncle Guo might be a bit better.

00:22:44.460 --> 00:22:45.740 line:80%
Mom's never beaten him.

00:22:45.940 --> 00:22:47.290 line:80%
Who's Uncle Guo?

00:22:48.020 --> 00:22:50.500 line:80%
He's the uncle
who grew up with your mom.

00:22:50.500 --> 00:22:52.570 line:80%
And also the junior brother
of mine and your Uncle Qi.

00:22:52.740 --> 00:22:54.330 line:80%
Uncle Qi's junior brother?

00:22:54.460 --> 00:22:55.890 line:80%
Is he also at the Qingque Sect?

00:23:07.940 --> 00:23:09.610 line:80%
We haven't heard from him in years.

00:23:10.130 --> 00:23:11.810 line:80%
Is he dead or alive?

00:23:12.090 --> 00:23:13.020 line:80%
Just tell us already.

00:23:13.570 --> 00:23:15.420 line:80%
Doesn't he know
how much we worry about him?

00:23:15.780 --> 00:23:17.570 line:80%
No news isn't always a bad thing.

00:23:18.120 --> 00:23:19.260 line:80%
Just imagine he's still alive.

00:23:25.460 --> 00:23:26.740 line:80%
Could Uncle Guo

00:23:27.290 --> 00:23:28.740 line:80%
have died here?

00:23:43.940 --> 00:23:44.790 line:80%
Mom,

00:23:44.930 --> 00:23:46.660 line:80%
do you know
why Dad went down the mountain?

00:23:47.220 --> 00:23:48.890 line:80%
He has his reasons for going.

00:23:49.660 --> 00:23:51.220 line:80%
Just focus on your cultivation.

00:23:51.500 --> 00:23:52.340 line:80%
Don't worry about it.

00:23:52.810 --> 00:23:54.090 line:80%
But Fengchi said

00:23:54.140 --> 00:23:56.500 line:80%
Dad suddenly left the mountain
after going to Chunling Cottage

00:23:56.520 --> 00:23:57.530 line:80%
the day before yesterday.

00:23:57.830 --> 00:23:58.940 line:80%
Don't you think that's strange?

00:23:59.530 --> 00:24:00.570 line:80%
And Yuzhi.

00:24:00.920 --> 00:24:02.260 line:80%
I haven't seen him in days either.

00:24:02.460 --> 00:24:04.420 line:80%
I thought he was
still recovering in seclusion.

00:24:04.780 --> 00:24:06.290 line:80%
But when I went to Chuitian Dock today,

00:24:06.530 --> 00:24:08.420 line:80%
there were only
two Guangtian Sect guards left.

00:24:09.050 --> 00:24:09.890 line:80%
They said

00:24:10.510 --> 00:24:11.890 line:80%
he went down to clear his head.

00:24:12.570 --> 00:24:13.410 line:80%
Speaking of which,

00:24:13.620 --> 00:24:15.130 line:80%
I haven't seen Cai Zhao in days either.

00:24:15.430 --> 00:24:17.180 line:80%
Could she have gone down
the mountain too?

00:24:18.660 --> 00:24:19.500 line:80%
No.

00:24:20.460 --> 00:24:22.220 line:80%
Did she actually leave with Yuzhi?

00:24:22.330 --> 00:24:23.170 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:24:31.660 --> 00:24:34.090 line:80%
Yuzhi would never act
so recklessly and disrespectfully

00:24:34.610 --> 00:24:35.570 line:80%
Yuzhi always acts

00:24:35.940 --> 00:24:37.330 line:80%
with caution and propriety,

00:24:37.500 --> 00:24:38.460 line:80%
honorable and upright.

00:24:38.840 --> 00:24:40.260 line:80%
If you still have feelings for him,

00:24:40.740 --> 00:24:42.290 line:80%
don't make wild guesses about him.

00:24:42.330 --> 00:24:43.370 line:80%
It'll only upset him.

00:24:45.080 --> 00:24:46.810 line:80%
I care about his injuries
every single day.

00:24:47.020 --> 00:24:47.980 line:80%
But he

00:24:48.990 --> 00:24:50.660 line:80%
snuck down the mountain
without a word.

00:24:51.180 --> 00:24:52.290 line:80%
Without even telling me.

00:24:54.130 --> 00:24:54.970 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:24:55.610 --> 00:24:56.450 line:80%
I already told you,

00:24:57.020 --> 00:24:58.420 line:80%
he doesn't have feelings for you.

00:24:59.090 --> 00:25:00.090 line:80%
Stop forcing it.

00:25:03.700 --> 00:25:04.540 line:80%
Mom.

00:25:06.890 --> 00:25:08.220 line:80%
We got engaged when I was nine.

00:25:08.530 --> 00:25:09.810 line:80%
It's been ten years.

00:25:10.020 --> 00:25:11.420 line:80%
I've trained hard every single day.

00:25:11.660 --> 00:25:13.740 line:80%
Lived in the Disciples' Dorm
like everyone else.

00:25:13.940 --> 00:25:15.330 line:80%
Just so I could be closer to him.

00:25:15.610 --> 00:25:16.530 line:80%
Hoping that one day,

00:25:16.720 --> 00:25:18.290 line:80%
I'd be worthy of him.
Someone so talented

00:25:18.460 --> 00:25:19.740 line:80%
and extraordinary.

00:25:20.840 --> 00:25:22.570 line:80%
I don't care about
being the Lady of Sect.

00:25:22.890 --> 00:25:24.130 line:80%
I just like him.

00:25:24.180 --> 00:25:25.290 line:80%
I like him so much.

00:25:25.700 --> 00:25:26.660 line:80%
So I keep forcing it!

00:25:39.780 --> 00:25:40.620 line:80%
Cai Zhao!

00:25:42.050 --> 00:25:42.890 line:80%
Not here.

00:25:44.330 --> 00:25:45.170 line:80%
Over there.

00:25:49.700 --> 00:25:51.100 line:80%
- Feicui.
- Feicui!

00:26:02.260 --> 00:26:03.100 line:80%
Where's Cai Zhao?

00:26:03.810 --> 00:26:05.610 line:80%
After that Body Shift incident,

00:26:05.700 --> 00:26:07.940 line:80%
milady's been holding in her anger.

00:26:08.120 --> 00:26:09.530 line:80%
It turns out more than ten years ago,

00:26:09.530 --> 00:26:11.260 line:80%
our Luoying Valley was besieged
by the demon sect,

00:26:11.260 --> 00:26:12.570 line:80%
and we almost all died.

00:26:12.820 --> 00:26:14.850 line:80%
It was all the doing of
the previous Lord of Qingque Sect

00:26:15.050 --> 00:26:16.500 line:80%
and his daughter.

00:26:17.320 --> 00:26:18.710 line:80%
Just thinking about it makes me angry.

00:26:19.050 --> 00:26:20.490 line:80%
This Qingque Sect,

00:26:20.660 --> 00:26:21.980 line:80%
is really not a place to stay.

00:26:22.370 --> 00:26:23.410 line:80%
- You...
- Shut up!

00:26:23.530 --> 00:26:24.780 line:80%
How dare a lowly maid

00:26:24.780 --> 00:26:26.050 line:80%
talk nonsense here?

00:26:26.610 --> 00:26:27.450 line:80%
Just tell me.

00:26:28.020 --> 00:26:29.130 line:80%
Where did Cai Zhao go?

00:26:31.130 --> 00:26:32.530 line:80%
For a disciple of Qingque Sect

00:26:32.950 --> 00:26:34.980 line:80%
to skip class and
sneak down the mountain for no reason

00:26:35.220 --> 00:26:36.810 line:80%
is to show open contempt for the sect

00:26:36.940 --> 00:26:37.930 line:80%
and defiance of the Master.

00:26:38.220 --> 00:26:40.180 line:80%
She deserves severe punishment,
expulsion from the sect!

00:26:42.290 --> 00:26:43.130 line:80%
Speak.

00:26:43.220 --> 00:26:44.530 line:80%
Where exactly has Cai Zhao gone?

00:26:46.180 --> 00:26:47.020 line:80%
Will you talk or not?

00:26:53.130 --> 00:26:53.970 line:80%
Xingjia, Lingbo.

00:26:54.700 --> 00:26:55.740 line:80%
Let's talk this out calmly.

00:26:56.780 --> 00:26:57.700 line:80%
Don't scare Feicui.

00:26:58.370 --> 00:26:59.220 line:80%
Zhuo.

00:26:59.290 --> 00:27:00.610 line:80%
She's just a maid.

00:27:00.680 --> 00:27:02.220 line:80%
A maid is still
a disciple of Luoying Valley.

00:27:02.720 --> 00:27:03.730 line:80%
We're all part of the Jianghu.

00:27:04.120 --> 00:27:05.330 line:80%
We don't judge people by their birth.

00:27:08.700 --> 00:27:09.540 line:80%
Let's go.

00:27:22.260 --> 00:27:23.100 line:80%
Feicui.

00:27:24.330 --> 00:27:25.180 line:80%
Zhuo.

00:27:25.850 --> 00:27:26.690 line:80%
Zhao.

00:27:27.420 --> 00:27:28.260 line:80%
Where exactly is she?

00:27:28.980 --> 00:27:30.290 line:80%
She isn't on the mountain.

00:27:30.420 --> 00:27:31.890 line:80%
But don't worry, Zhuo.

00:27:32.220 --> 00:27:33.420 line:80%
She's with Yuzhi.

00:27:33.500 --> 00:27:34.570 line:80%
She'll be fine.

00:27:37.180 --> 00:27:38.130 line:80%
Zhuo.

00:27:41.500 --> 00:27:42.340 line:80%
Then I'll be off.

00:28:02.690 --> 00:28:03.940 line:80%
I've been waiting for you, Lord.

00:28:09.220 --> 00:28:10.070 line:80%
Yunke.

00:28:10.130 --> 00:28:11.050 line:80%
Come, have some tea.

00:28:11.330 --> 00:28:12.170 line:80%
Shijun.

00:28:12.270 --> 00:28:13.420 line:80%
You left days earlier than me,

00:28:13.570 --> 00:28:14.410 line:80%
so why haven't you

00:28:14.740 --> 00:28:15.940 line:80%
entered the Hanhai Mountains yet?

00:28:17.260 --> 00:28:18.330 line:80%
The entrance is sealed.

00:28:18.420 --> 00:28:19.260 line:80%
Can't get in.

00:28:19.810 --> 00:28:20.780 line:80%
I'm guessing

00:28:20.890 --> 00:28:23.500 line:80%
Mr. Mu and Nie Zhe got into a fight.

00:28:23.500 --> 00:28:25.090 line:80%
Then how do you still
have time to sip tea here?

00:28:26.610 --> 00:28:27.570 line:80%
What's the rush?

00:28:29.500 --> 00:28:32.180 line:80%
When Pingshu was Zhao's age,

00:28:32.330 --> 00:28:33.660 line:80%
she could fight her way in and out

00:28:33.660 --> 00:28:35.130 line:80%
of the Youming Path
multiple times.

00:28:35.180 --> 00:28:36.020 line:80%
Besides,

00:28:36.090 --> 00:28:37.460 line:80%
as long as we lay low,

00:28:37.500 --> 00:28:38.850 line:80%
no one will know their identities.

00:28:39.030 --> 00:28:39.970 line:80%
That just makes it safer.

00:28:40.600 --> 00:28:42.060 line:80%
Come on, come down and have some tea.

00:28:42.180 --> 00:28:43.020 line:80%
Let me tell you,

00:28:43.180 --> 00:28:44.700 line:80%
I spent quite a bit on this tea.

00:28:45.090 --> 00:28:46.330 line:80%
The Spring Equinox Maojian Tea.

00:28:46.420 --> 00:28:48.050 line:80%
One sip is worth ten taels of silver.

00:28:52.420 --> 00:28:53.260 line:80%
Give it a try.

00:28:58.370 --> 00:28:59.270 line:80%
Yunke,

00:28:59.290 --> 00:29:00.130 line:80%
please.

00:29:05.220 --> 00:29:06.700 line:80%
Pingshu wrote earlier that

00:29:07.260 --> 00:29:08.570 line:80%
Zhao kept asking him about

00:29:09.030 --> 00:29:10.460 line:80%
the whereabouts of the Jade Sunflower.

00:29:11.050 --> 00:29:11.890 line:80%
This time,

00:29:11.950 --> 00:29:13.370 line:80%
she went down the mountain with Yuzhi.

00:29:13.660 --> 00:29:15.180 line:80%
Straight for the Hanhai Mountains.

00:29:15.810 --> 00:29:17.020 line:80%
Could the Jade Sunflower

00:29:17.420 --> 00:29:18.530 line:80%
really be in the demon sect?

00:29:18.780 --> 00:29:20.090 line:80%
Knowing Pingshu's personality,

00:29:20.260 --> 00:29:22.090 line:80%
she might have really returned it.

00:29:26.570 --> 00:29:28.890 line:80%
No one knows the two kids
went down the mountain together,

00:29:29.180 --> 00:29:30.020 line:80%
right?

00:29:30.780 --> 00:29:32.780 line:80%
After all, they're both unmarried.

00:29:32.780 --> 00:29:33.620 line:80%
What if...

00:29:33.620 --> 00:29:34.570 line:80%
I came alone this time,

00:29:34.740 --> 00:29:36.260 line:80%
just to keep things quiet.

00:29:45.090 --> 00:29:45.940 line:80%
I only hope

00:29:46.420 --> 00:29:47.940 line:80%
they all stay safe.

00:29:55.570 --> 00:29:59.290 line:80%
(My parents are still alive,
when can I go home?)

00:30:02.130 --> 00:30:03.500 line:80%
(The softening powder)

00:30:04.260 --> 00:30:05.890 line:80%
(is getting stronger.)

00:30:06.850 --> 00:30:08.610 line:80%
(Am I going to die here too?)

00:30:21.270 --> 00:30:22.610 line:80%
You overexerted your mind and spirit

00:30:22.850 --> 00:30:23.940 line:80%
fighting Duan Jiuxiu.

00:30:24.020 --> 00:30:25.260 line:80%
You have stagnant energy in your body.

00:30:25.530 --> 00:30:26.780 line:80%
It needs to be released soon.

00:30:27.220 --> 00:30:28.500 line:80%
There are no medicinal herbs here.

00:30:29.020 --> 00:30:30.090 line:80%
Back at the sect. I'll handle it.

00:30:30.320 --> 00:30:31.850 line:80%
I'll teach you
an internal mindful way.

00:30:31.890 --> 00:30:32.750 line:80%
Try using your energy.

00:30:32.810 --> 00:30:34.940 line:80%
Is this the Mu clan's
secret internal mindful way?

00:30:35.090 --> 00:30:35.930 line:80%
You could say that.

00:30:36.370 --> 00:30:38.020 line:80%
This mindful way
was created by my father.

00:30:38.220 --> 00:30:39.780 line:80%
It's called the Innate Circulation.

00:30:39.820 --> 00:30:41.370 line:80%
It works wonders for
injuries and poison.

00:30:42.220 --> 00:30:43.370 line:80%
If not for this mindful way,

00:30:43.740 --> 00:30:44.580 line:80%
over a year ago,

00:30:44.680 --> 00:30:46.050 line:80%
I would've died in the Hanhai Mountains.

00:30:50.750 --> 00:30:52.290 line:80%
New moon on the third, it gleams bright.

00:30:54.320 --> 00:30:55.780 line:80%
Zhen aligns with Geng, toward the West.

00:30:59.920 --> 00:31:01.290 line:80%
On the eighth day,
Dui with Ding.

00:31:02.180 --> 00:31:04.530 line:80%
The crescent, taut as a silken cord.

00:31:06.220 --> 00:31:07.890 line:80%
On the fifteenth day,
Qian forms complete.

00:31:09.700 --> 00:31:11.940 line:80%
Full and bright,
align with Jia, toward the East.

00:31:16.980 --> 00:31:18.260 line:80%
(It actually seems to work.)

00:31:19.810 --> 00:31:21.220 line:80%
(Finally, there's a way out.)

00:31:33.500 --> 00:31:34.340 line:80%
Who are you?

00:31:34.500 --> 00:31:35.740 line:80%
Have you seen the corpse slaves?

00:31:36.370 --> 00:31:37.210 line:80%
A ghost.

00:31:37.840 --> 00:31:38.810 line:80%
I've never seen a ghost.

00:31:45.290 --> 00:31:46.700 line:80%
We'll see where you can run when you

00:31:46.700 --> 00:31:47.540 line:80%
get to the Underworld.

00:31:48.220 --> 00:31:49.290 line:80%
Kill me.

00:31:50.020 --> 00:31:51.570 line:80%
Then your Chief will never get

00:31:51.570 --> 00:31:53.220 line:80%
the treasure for
his divine skill cultivation.

00:31:53.810 --> 00:31:54.850 line:80%
What treasure?

00:32:01.460 --> 00:32:02.300 line:80%
A month ago,

00:32:02.980 --> 00:32:03.820 line:80%
I…

00:32:03.980 --> 00:32:05.220 line:80%
I ran into three people.

00:32:05.500 --> 00:32:06.610 line:80%
One of them said

00:32:06.980 --> 00:32:08.220 line:80%
he was…

00:32:09.220 --> 00:32:10.420 line:80%
Elder from the Li Sect.

00:32:11.290 --> 00:32:13.090 line:80%
Elder Tianji, Duan Jiuxiu.

00:32:13.980 --> 00:32:15.260 line:80%
Where are they now?

00:32:15.780 --> 00:32:17.890 line:80%
They were killed by people
from the Six Sects of Beichen.

00:32:18.700 --> 00:32:19.570 line:80%
Before they died,

00:32:20.050 --> 00:32:21.500 line:80%
they gave me a bottle of something.

00:32:21.710 --> 00:32:22.850 line:80%
Said it was for cultivating...

00:32:22.860 --> 00:32:23.970 line:80%
It called...

00:32:24.940 --> 00:32:25.940 line:80%
Ziwei Method.

00:32:26.700 --> 00:32:27.540 line:80%
They also said

00:32:27.660 --> 00:32:29.700 line:80%
if I offered this treasure
to the Chief of Li Sect,

00:32:29.840 --> 00:32:30.700 line:80%
I'd get a huge reward.

00:32:30.780 --> 00:32:32.460 line:80%
I'm willing to
hand over that treasure now.

00:32:33.460 --> 00:32:34.660 line:80%
All I ask is that you spare me.

00:32:34.890 --> 00:32:35.730 line:80%
Let me live.

00:32:36.890 --> 00:32:38.330 line:80%
Where is the treasure now?

00:32:38.570 --> 00:32:40.460 line:80%
I hid it in the woods of
the Hanhai Mountains.

00:32:41.090 --> 00:32:42.530 line:80%
I can take you there right now.

00:32:43.820 --> 00:32:45.020 line:80%
Trying to trick me?

00:32:45.500 --> 00:32:46.820 line:80%
Elder Tianji,

00:32:47.370 --> 00:32:48.660 line:80%
such a suspicious person,

00:32:49.610 --> 00:32:51.330 line:80%
would never hand a treasure to

00:32:51.700 --> 00:32:53.420 line:80%
a girl he doesn't even know.

00:32:53.610 --> 00:32:55.290 line:80%
It wasn't Elder Tianji
who gave it to me.

00:32:56.090 --> 00:32:57.610 line:80%
It was someone called

00:32:58.740 --> 00:33:00.260 line:80%
Qinong, a beautiful lady.

00:33:00.680 --> 00:33:01.740 line:80%
She secretly hid it for me.

00:33:02.020 --> 00:33:04.290 line:80%
She said Elder Tianji
had turned against her,

00:33:05.290 --> 00:33:06.940 line:80%
and she couldn't survive anymore.

00:33:07.330 --> 00:33:09.740 line:80%
So she asked me to
pass a message to the Chief.

00:33:29.220 --> 00:33:30.260 line:80%
Bring him up here!

00:33:32.130 --> 00:33:32.970 line:80%
Help me!

00:33:36.330 --> 00:33:37.500 line:80%
Where's the treasure?

00:33:38.090 --> 00:33:38.980 line:80%
If you don't talk,

00:33:39.260 --> 00:33:40.420 line:80%
then I'll throw you in.

00:33:40.890 --> 00:33:42.500 line:80%
So this is how you refine corpse slaves.

00:33:43.330 --> 00:33:44.810 line:80%
You've really lost all humanity!

00:33:45.850 --> 00:33:46.690 line:80%
One.

00:33:46.890 --> 00:33:47.730 line:80%
Two.

00:34:02.980 --> 00:34:04.290 line:80%
If I die, we die together!

00:34:08.490 --> 00:34:09.330 line:80%
Zhao.

00:34:09.450 --> 00:34:10.290 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:34:15.660 --> 00:34:17.260 line:80%
Zhao, are you hurt?

00:34:17.450 --> 00:34:18.290 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:34:18.650 --> 00:34:19.780 line:80%
Outside attack.

00:34:19.970 --> 00:34:20.810 line:80%
We need to go now.

00:34:26.060 --> 00:34:26.900 line:80%
- Get up.
- Get up.

00:34:27.330 --> 00:34:28.370 line:80%
- Get up.
- Thanks, Miss Feng.

00:34:28.370 --> 00:34:29.230 line:80%
Please, get up.

00:34:29.290 --> 00:34:30.410 line:80%
- Get up.
- Upholding justice

00:34:30.410 --> 00:34:32.220 line:80%
is what we in the Jianghu should do.

00:34:32.450 --> 00:34:33.620 line:80%
No need to stand on ceremony.

00:34:56.720 --> 00:34:58.540 line:80%
Mr. Mu, the forced attack
triggered the mechanism.

00:34:58.540 --> 00:34:59.490 line:80%
This place is collapsing!

00:35:09.580 --> 00:35:10.420 line:80%
Li Yi.

00:35:11.330 --> 00:35:12.330 line:80%
Wasn't he stationed at

00:35:12.330 --> 00:35:13.580 line:80%
the Xuanwu Altar with Yu Huiyin?

00:35:14.850 --> 00:35:17.010 line:80%
So this is
where they make corpse slaves.

00:35:17.180 --> 00:35:18.450 line:80%
Monstrous curs.

00:35:18.480 --> 00:35:20.140 line:80%
How many innocent believers
did they seize?

00:35:20.220 --> 00:35:21.620 line:80%
How many corpse slaves have they made?

00:35:29.970 --> 00:35:30.810 line:80%
Sunshine Blade.

00:35:33.410 --> 00:35:34.250 line:80%
Zhao.

00:35:35.121 --> 00:35:45.781 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

