00:36:31.031 --> 00:36:35.321 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:36:35.981 --> 00:36:40.011 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:36:40.326 --> 00:36:45.451 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:36:46.026 --> 00:36:50.836 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
